OL,3,CTata and British Steel bosses to sit
OL,4,Con new Government steel council
OL,6,FThe chief executives of Tata Steel and
OL,7,FBritish Steel, along with the GMB
OL,8,FTrade Union and devolved government
OL,9,Fministers, will be among the members
OL,10,Fset to meet regularly.
OL,12,FLast year, Tata Steel said it was
OL,13,Freplacing traditional blast furnaces
OL,14,Fwith an electric arc furnace at its
OL,15,Fbiggest UK site in Port Talbot, Wales.
OL,17,FTraditional steelmaking ceased in
OL,18,FSeptember, with thousands of workers
OL,19,Flosing their jobs.
