OL,3,CTata and British Steel bosses to sit
OL,4,Con new Government steel council
OL,6,FBritish Steel also announced it would
OL,7,Fclose blast furnaces in Scunthorpe in
OL,8,F2023, and unveiled plans to roll out a
OL,9,Fless polluting electric arc furnace.
OL,11,FThe plans, which are greener but
OL,12,Frequire fewer workers to keep them
OL,13,Fgoing, raised fears over potentially
OL,14,Fthousands of job losses.
OL,16,FThe Labour Government has vowed to
OL,17,Fspend #2.5 billion "to rebuild the
OL,18,Fsteel industry".
