OL,4,Con new Government steel council
OL,6,FThe council will also discuss how to
OL,7,Fallocate the up to #2.5 billion
OL,8,Ffunding.
OL,10,F"The industry and steel communities
OL,11,Fhave had enough of lurching from
OL,12,Fcrisis to crisis ` this Government
OL,13,Fwill take the action needed to place
OL,14,Fsteel on a secure footing for the long
OL,15,Fterm," Mr Reynolds said.
