OL,3,CTata and British Steel bosses to sit
OL,4,Con new Government steel council
OL,6,F"With the launch of the Steel Council
OL,7,Fwe're placing workers and local
OL,8,Fcommunities at the heart of our plans
OL,9,Fas we bring forward #2.5 billion of
OL,10,Finvestment to secure growth right
OL,11,Facross the country."
OL,13,FGareth Stace, director general of
OL,14,Ftrade group UK Steel, said: "The
OL,15,Festablishment of the Steel Council
OL,16,Fmarks a defining moment for the future
OL,17,Fof steelmaking in Britain.
